T02D3415:81b-1: lo ke n'a tha s'a dha nam /
T02D3415:81b-4: 'jig rten mgon po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3415:81b-5: rnal 'byor rim pa sngon ma bzhin //
T02D3415:82a-1: yi yi ge las byung ba'i //
T02D3415:82a-2: ral ba'i cod pan gyis brgyan pa //
T02D3415:82a-3: ral pa'i mthar gnas rdo rje chos //
T02D3415:82a-4: nad rnams ma lus 'joms byed pa //
T02D3415:82a-5: phyag g-yas mchog sbyin de bzhin du //
T02D3415:82a-6: g-yon pa na ni padma bsnams //
T02D3415:82a-7: rol pa'i stabs kyis yang dag bzhugs//
T02D3415:82a-9: mchog sbyin autpal phyag na bsnams //
T02D3415:82a-10: zhi ba'i sgrol ma g-yas phyogs bzhugs //
T02D3415:82a-11: de nas rta mgrin g-yon phyogs na //
T02D3415:82a-12: phyag 'tshal ba dang dbyug pa'i phyag / drag chen sku mdog dmar po ste //
T02D3415:82a-13: stag gi pags pa'i na bza' dgyes //
T02D3415:82a-14: de bzhin cho ga yang dag ldan //
T02D3415:82a-15: 'jig rten mgon po rab bsgoms na //
T02D3415:82a-16: nyon mongs dri ma kun las 'das //
T02D3415:82a-17: yid kyi shing rta gang bar 'gyur //
